  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "Credibility assessment for CFD-based hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. Model Risk Level 5. Thirteen credibility factors evaluated under ASME V&V 40-2018. Submitted under Minimal profile; use-scope documentation deferred to supplementary filing.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-req-001",
