    "rationale": "Package accepted for registry ingestion under Minimal profile. All thirteen credibility factors have been populated with required and achieved levels. Six factors remain not-assessed, reflecting known epistemic gaps at MRL 5 that are documented for follow-on resolution. Minimal profile does not mandate a Context of Use object; use-scope definition is deferred to the next assessment cycle.",
